 "remarks": "Stunning 4-bedroom, 4.1-bath Colonial on .77 acres completely reimagined &amp; renovated by Nordic Custom Builders offers exceptional craftsmanship &amp; modern luxury throughout. Gracious layout features formal living &amp; dining rooms with fireplace &amp; French doors opening to expansive bluestone patio &amp; pool. Spectacular office showcases vaulted shiplap ceiling, marble wet bar with wine refrigerator &amp; French doors to backyard. Custom moldings throughout. Chef&apos;s kitchen beautifully appointed with Thermador appliances, Sub-Zero refrigerator &amp; freezer, custom cabinetry, banquette seating &amp; an additional wet bar with wine fridge &amp; ice maker. French doors lead to screened porch with removable plexiglass panels for warmth, ideal for effortless indoor-outdoor living. Sophisticated family room features oversized windows, custom built-ins &amp; fireplace. Integrated audio system runs throughout the home. Luxurious primary suite lined with custom built-ins offers oversized walk-in closet &amp; marble bath with steam shower &amp; heated floors. Three additional bedrooms with custom closets &amp; two marble baths with heated floors complete 2nd floor. Finished lower level includes a full bath and two large flexible spaces for gym, playroom, media room or fifth bedroom. Step outside to enjoy a meticulously landscaped lawn with new Gunite pool, hot tub, &amp; pool house. Every detail in this home is new - all windows, doors, 10&quot; white oak floors, HVAC/furnace, cedar roof, irrigation, landscaping/lighting &amp; more!",
